Hi 
It was great chatting with you earlier this morning! Attached you'll find a smaller zip folder containing just the tax returns, 
for each year from 2015 to 2019. You shouldn't need a password to open the folders, but in case it prompts you, the 
password defense counsel provided us is: 
The entirety of the Financial Report Appendices are still loading onto USAFx, and it appears as if there is less than a third 
left to download. I'm estimating it will take about another hour to an hour and a half for everything to finish downloading 
there. Once they've downloaded, I'll share the folder with you. 
Thank you so much for your patience and please let me know if you encounter any issues viewing these tax 
returns!
